- Database
  - Parties Table
    - id
    - name
    - votes

- Client
  Enter the party to vote for in the format (VOTE <<party-name>>)
  Display whatever response comes from the server


- Server
  - Gets the data from the client (VOTE <<part-name>>)
  - If the data is not in the asked format send "Please enter vote in right format" message to the client
  - Check whether the party represented by the party-name exists in the database or no
  - If it does not exist, send "Please enter the right party name" message to the client
  - If the party exist, increment the vote in the database by 1 and send "Vote successful" message
  to the client